        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520"> 
            <head>Scope and Content Note</head> 
            <p>Correspondence, articles, typescripts, notes, maps, charts,
                slides, and other materials, written or collected by 
                Schilling, relating to the history and development of 
                various forts in Arizona and New Mexico. Contains 
                photostat copies of War Dept. files of New Mexico post 
                returns, 1852-1884, outline index of Arizona military 
                posts giving locations and dates of occupation, and 
                descriptive report and maps for Fort Apache, Fort Grant, 
                Fort Bowie, Fort Lowell, Fort McDowell, and Fort Mojave. 
                Slides, taken ca. 1958-1960, are of both historical 
                photographs and contemporary sites of forts in Arizona and
                New Mexico. Also present are notes, typescripts, and 
                slides concerning Al Sieber, slides of Apache Indians, and
                charts which list posts alphabetically and chronologically
                by date activated.</p> 
        </scopecontent>
